## <a id='about'></a>About Compute Profiles

<%= vars.k8s_runtime_abbr %> admins can define
compute settings such as CPU, memory, ephemeral disk, and persistent disk
for Kubernetes clusters with a compute profile.

You can also define availability zones (AZs) using a compute profile.


